    "description": "让自己沉浸在一个可以按下按钮的世界里。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1899820/extras/031285e01b5ac6659238b5f26dc21e6f.poster.avif?t=1728505859\" width=472 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1899820/extras/031285e01b5ac6659238b5f26dc21e6f.webm?t=1728505859\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1899820/extras/031285e01b5ac6659238b5f26dc21e6f.mp4?t=1728505859\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>你从来没有在虚拟现实中像这样按过按钮。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1899820/extras/c3d65fd194a9c15cd287cfabf2fbcf50.poster.avif?t=1728505859\" width=472 height=198 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1899820/extras/c3d65fd194a9c15cd287cfabf2fbcf50.webm?t=1728505859\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1899820/extras/c3d65fd194a9c15cd287cfabf2fbcf50.mp4?t=1728505859\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>赚取积分来升级和自动化。在增量中没有任何 &quot;空闲&quot;。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1899820/extras/223a35a77005137a19e1b3b72a619a11.poster.avif?t=1728505859\" width=472 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1899820/extras/223a35a77005137a19e1b3b72a619a11.webm?t=1728505859\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1899820/extras/223a35a77005137a19e1b3b72a619a11.mp4?t=1728505859\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>增加是唯一重要的事情吗？在这个实验性的VR冒险中找出来。<br><br><strong>主动递增的游戏方式</strong> <br>用你的身体使数字向唯一重要的方向发展，即向上！这就是增量。递增是一种活跃的、动态的VR体验。<br><br><strong>微小的动作，巨大的结果</strong> <br>人类大小的终端控制着巨大的、利用VR的规模和奇迹感的机器。<br><br><strong>老少皆宜</strong> <br>《增量》是一种非暴力, 没有对话的体验。",
